the naked maja is a 1958 italian-french-american co-production made by s.g.c. , titanus films , and united artists .   this historical film recounting of the romance between the painter francisco goya and the duchess of alba was directed by henry koster , and produced by silvio clementelli and goffredo lombardo .   the screenplay was by norman corwin , giorgio prosperi and albert lewin based on a story by oscar saul and talbot jennings .   the music score was by angelo lavagnino and the cinematography by giuseppe rotunno .   the film stars ava gardner and anthony franciosa with amedeo nazzari , gino cervi , lea padovani , massimo serato , and a largely italian cast .   it is based on a novel by noel gerson .